<div class="content means imeans" data-group="imeans" id="basicmean-wrapper">
    <h1><b class="title active" id="basicmean" data-group="imeans">基本释义</b><span class="seg"></span>
                <a href="javascript:watchit()" class="title disactive" data-for="detailmean">详细解释</a>
        <span class="seg"></span>
            </h1>
    <div class="tab-content">
    <dl><dd><ol><li><p> [vast]∶[区域] 宽阔而弘大</p><p>广大地区</p></li><li><p> [extensive;large-scale;widespread]</p></li><li><p> (范围、规模)巨大</p><p>掀起广大的技术革新热潮</p></li><li><p> 范围很宽的</p><p>广大农村</p></li><li><p> [numerous]∶数目很多的</p><p>广大知识分子</p></li></ol></dd></dl>
    </div>
